<div class="alert-box-info">
    <h3 class="heading-size-3 font-2"><i class="alert_icon fa fa-info-circle"></i>Tip: Combine commonly reused modifiers</h3>
    <p>If you are commonly reusing the same combination of modifiers multiple times, you can combine them into a new modifier:</p>

<pre><code>@include buttons((
